                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-200-off1114 t18300415-200-cd1115"></join>, 1 looking-glass, value 2l. 10s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18300415-200-victim1781" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
